 href=\"https://lih.kg/2091697\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2091697</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T21:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實班撚屌係咪想復出<br />\n見到格黎有人開PO屌慕容"},{"pid":"ac75b025d2d831b6d9531047528c3a49ab325a55","tid":2169640,"uid":132986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e6abb5e3ca8239dca5819833614520efb4e16822","tid":2169640,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3192a2ede84742d5817856e702656c5cbeffa28","tid":2169640,"uid":132986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T21:48:07.000Z","msg":"［打擊網絡垃圾］屎萊姆同屎炮車試水溫想復出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2144946\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2144946</a><br />\n<br />\n［狂賀］屎家軍夾公仔舖違反停業令  連續兩日被爆格<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136037\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136037</a><br />\n<br />\n［細b知法犯法］乜紅店CGA有特權可以係武肺期間繼續營業架？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2132739\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2132739</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屎萊姆一而再再而三擺Auman上枱，Auman已經成為屎家軍既condom<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2076779\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2076779</a><br />\n<br />\n［分享喜悅］屎萊姆你件垃圾輸唔起就唔好租台呃人錢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2091697\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2091697</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T21:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實班撚屌係咪想復出<br />\n見到格黎有人開PO屌慕容"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T21:53:55.000Z","msg":"班冚家剷一直用唔同方法試水溫<br />\n要report屎家軍fb ig yt<br />\n罷買罷用屎家軍既sponsor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099131bc8403b90e188fe2965c37a027be5ad526","tid":2169640,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T22:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83a3392f050c352e020dd45a440ea691b4888b1d","tid":2169640,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"099131bc8403b90e188fe2965c37a027be5ad526","tid":2169640,"uid":60916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T22:43:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T23:20:46.000Z","msg":"李柱銘：「<span class=\"red\"><strong>既然政府押後選舉，立法會任期延長，民意授權亦因而延長</strong></span>，該現任議員的選民肯定不會希望他們自動消失。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n泛民要用比較德高望重既老屎忽去講啲咁既歪理去說服民眾延續政黨壽命<br />\n你就知班撚屌已經技窮<br />\n押後選舉根據基本法只可押後14日<br />\n過左14日唔選就係非法<br />\n如果班友拒絕委任, 唔搞補選又係非法<br />\n如果班友拒絕委任, 政府篤廿幾個人入去, 又係非法<br />\n根本拒絕委任就將個dilemma俾返政府<br />\n屌喇星成班友磨爛蓆"}]}